---

<Layout title="Pricing | Kalthoff Performance" description="Choose the plan that fits your fitness goals.">
  <section class="py-16 min-h-screen bg-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bebas text-center mb-6 tracking-wider text-white">There are multiple ways we can work together<br />to reach your fitness goals</h1>
      <div class="bg-black rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 md:p-12 mb-10">
        <p class="italic text-lg text-white text-center mb-2">
          <span class="font-semibold">Depending on what your goals are, I have a plan that will <span class='font-bold'>fit your lifestyle</span>.</span> Some people are self-starters - they receive a plan and go for it with little guidance needed. Others need support along the way. Regardless of where you see yourself, <span class='font-bold'>we'll make it work!</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Responsive Pricing Tiers -->
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:gap-0 md:grid-cols-3 mb-8">
        <!-- Tier 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center p-6 md:border-r md:border-gray-300">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-bebas mb-2">Tier 1</div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold mb-4">Standard Programming</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl">✔️</span>
            <span>App Access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-red-600 text-2xl">❌</span>
            <span>Intro Call</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 mb-2 w-full">
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>1-3 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$50</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>4-6 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$70</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Tier 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center p-6 md:border-r md:border-gray-300">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-bebas mb-2">Tier 2</div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold mb-4">Custom Programming</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl">✔️</span>
            <span>App Access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl">✔️</span>
            <span>Intro Call</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 mb-2 w-full">
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>1-3 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$120</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>4-6 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$150</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Tier 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center p-6">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-bebas mb-2">Tier 3</div>
          <div class="text-base font-semibold mb-4">Highly Customized Programming</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl">✔️</span>
            <span>App Access</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 text-2xl">✔️</span>
            <span>Intro Call</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 mb-2 w-full">
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>1-3 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$200</span></div>
            <div class="flex justify-between w-full"><span>4-6 Weekly Workouts</span><span class="font-bold">$250</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Programming Details Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bebas mb-10 tracking-wider text-white">Additional Programming Details</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Monthly Membership -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full border-4 border-lime-400 flex items-center justify-center text-center text-lg font-bold bg-white shadow" style="border-width: 4px;">
              <span class="block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bebas">Monthly<br />Membership</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Add on to any program</h3>
            <p class="mb-2 text-white">Weekly, Bi-Weekly or Monthly 30 minute, 1on1 video coaching calls to tackle fitness, nutrition or injury related program questions. Ranges from <span class="font-semibold">$75-$300 / month</span>. This is ideal for someone who wants:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 text-gray-200">
              <li>Consistent program modification</li>
              <li>Video review of exercise technique</li>
              <li>Nutrition planning and guidance to target your goals</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="border-t-4 border-cyan-300 my-2" />
        <!-- Tier 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full border-4 border-cyan-400 flex items-center justify-center text-center text-lg font-bold bg-white shadow">
              <span class="block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bebas">Tier 1</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Standardized programming</h3>
            <p class="text-white">These are non-individualized programs that emphasize full body strength, athleticism, resilience to injury and general health and wellness</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="border-t-4 border-yellow-400 my-2" />
        <!-- Tier 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full border-4 border-yellow-400 flex items-center justify-center text-center text-lg font-bold bg-white shadow">
              <span class="block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bebas">Tier 2</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Choose your workout schedule</h3>
            <p class="mb-2 text-white">These are individualized programs that are built specifically for you and include:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 text-gray-200">
              <li>Individualized injury prevention and corrective movements for you</li>
              <li>Targeted gym and endurance-based plans for the sports and activities you love</li>
              <li>Tailored recovery so you can feel your best</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="border-t-4 border-orange-400 my-2" />
        <!-- Tier 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full border-4 border-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center text-center text-lg font-bold bg-white shadow">
              <span class="block text-xl md:text-2xl font-bebas">Tier 3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Choose your workout schedule</h3>
            <p class="mb-2 text-white">These are highly individualized programs that are built to accommodate your lifestyle, goals and schedule:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 text-gray-200">
              <li>Individualized programming including all tier 2 services plus additional customization</li>
              <li>Targeted gym / home based plans that fit into your schedule</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Download PDF Bottom -->
  <div class="flex justify-center py-12 bg-black">
    <a href={pdfUrl} download class="inline-block bg-blue-900 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bebas tracking-wider hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 shadow-lg">
      Download Full Price Guide (PDF)
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout> 